{"word":"G1971 - ἐπιποθέω - epipothéō - ep-ee-poth-eh'-o - Desire","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιποθέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epipothéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-poth-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Desire</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வாஞ்சையாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to long for, desire"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <b>&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>potheo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>yearn</i>); to <i>dote upon</i>, that is, <i>intensely crave</i> possession (lawfully or wrongfully): - (earnestly) desire (greatly), (greatly) long (after), lust.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}